page.title: 12HOUSING.
page.content: {Local Housing in Leeman Rd Area. Most houses around here are terraced houses.There are a few semi detached houses around our end in Chudleigh Rd.Our house is a terraced house of course.We have 3 rooms down stairs.Outside the yard is long and thin.We have a shed at the bottom of it.It is quite small.Wayne and I lock our bikes at the top of our yard.There is one big detached house in our area, that is up Jubilee Terrace and it is near our church.It is the vicarage.There are about five diferent sorts of terraced houses in the Leeman Rd area. One has 3 rooms downstairs and 3 rooms upstairs; and the second 3 downstairs and 2 up;the third has 4 down and 2 up; the fourth has 2 down 3 up;and the last has 2 down and 4 up.They don't have any gardens.
